  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.1 RSI原理\n",
    "\n",
    "**RSI（Relative Strength Index）** 用于衡量股价变动的速度和幅度，判断市场是否处于超买或超卖状态。\n",
    "\n",
    "**计算公式**：\n",
    "```\n",
    "RSI = 100 - (100 / (1 + RS))\n",
    "RS = 平均上涨幅度 / 平均下跌幅度\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**判断标准**：\n",
    "- RSI > 70：超买区域，价格可能回调\n",
    "- RSI < 30：超卖区域，价格可能反弹\n",
    "- RSI = 50：多空分界线\n",
    "\n",
    "**常用参数**：N = 14（14个交易日）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 2.2 实现RSI计算函数 ==========\n",
    "def calculate_rsi(df, n=14):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算RSI指标\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：\n",
    "    - df: DataFrame，包含'close'列\n",
    "    - n: 计算周期，默认14\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回：\n",
    "    - rsi: Series，RSI值\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 计算每日涨跌幅\n",
    "    delta = df['close'].diff()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 分离上涨和下跌\n",
    "    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0)  # 上涨部分\n",
    "    loss = -delta.where(delta < 0, 0)  # 下跌部分（取正值）\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算平均上涨和平均下跌（使用简单移动平均）\n",
    "    avg_gain = gain.rolling(window=n, min_periods=n).mean()\n",
    "    avg_loss = loss.rolling(window=n, min_periods=n).mean()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算RS和RSI\n",
    "    rs = avg_gain / avg_loss\n",
    "    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return rsi\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ RSI计算函数已定义\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 2.3 计算RSI并添加到数据框 ==========\n",
    "df['RSI_14'] = calculate_rsi(df, n=14)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ RSI计算完成\")\n",
    "print(f\"   RSI范围：{df['RSI_14'].min():.2f} ~ {df['RSI_14'].max():.2f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"   最新RSI：{df['RSI_14'].iloc[-1]:.2f}\")\n",
    "df[['trade_date', 'close', 'RSI_14']].tail(10)"
   ]
