    "## Part 3：MACD（移动平均收敛/发散指标）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.1 MACD原理\n",
    "\n",
    "**MACD（Moving Average Convergence Divergence）** 通过快慢均线的离散、聚合表征当前买卖能量。\n",
    "\n",
    "**计算公式**：\n",
    "```\n",
    "MACD线 = EMA(close, 12) - EMA(close, 26)\n",
    "信号线 = EMA(MACD线, 9)\n",
    "柱状图 = MACD线 - 信号线\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "其中EMA（指数移动平均）计算公式：\n",
    "```\n",
    "EMA(n) = 今日收盘价 × (2/(n+1)) + 昨日EMA × (1 - 2/(n+1))\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**判断标准**：\n",
    "- MACD > 0：多头市场（快线上穿慢线）\n",
    "- MACD < 0：空头市场（快线下穿慢线）\n",
    "- MACD上穿信号线：黄金交叉，买入信号\n",
    "- MACD下穿信号线：死亡交叉，卖出信号"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 3.2 实现EMA计算函数 ==========\n",
    "def calculate_ema(df, n):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算指数移动平均（EMA）\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：\n",
    "    - df: DataFrame，包含'close'列\n",
    "    - n: EMA周期\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回：\n",
    "    - ema: Series，EMA值\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    return df['close'].ewm(span=n, adjust=False).mean()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ EMA计算函数已定义\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 3.3 实现MACD计算函数 ==========\n",
    "def calculate_macd(df, fast=12, slow=26, signal=9):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算MACD指标\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：\n",
    "    - df: DataFrame，包含'close'列\n",
    "    - fast: 快线周期，默认12\n",
    "    - slow: 慢线周期，默认26\n",
    "    - signal: 信号线周期，默认9\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回：\n",
    "    - macd: Series，MACD线\n",
    "    - signal_line: Series，信号线\n",
    "    - histogram: Series，柱状图\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 计算快慢EMA\n",
    "    ema_fast = calculate_ema(df, fast)\n",
    "    ema_slow = calculate_ema(df, slow)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算MACD线\n",
    "    macd = ema_fast - ema_slow\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算信号线\n",
    "    signal_line = macd.ewm(span=signal, adjust=False).mean()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算柱状图\n",
    "    histogram = macd - signal_line\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return macd, signal_line, histogram\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ MACD计算函数已定义\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 3.4 计算MACD并添加到数据框 ==========\n",
    "df['MACD'], df['MACD_signal'], df['MACD_hist'] = calculate_macd(df)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ MACD计算完成\")\n",
    "print(f\"   最新MACD：{df['MACD'].iloc[-1]:.2f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"   最新信号线：{df['MACD_signal'].iloc[-1]:.2f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"   最新柱状图：{df['MACD_hist'].iloc[-1]:.2f}\")\n",
    "df[['trade_date', 'close', 'MACD', 'MACD_signal', 'MACD_hist']].tail(10)"
   ]
