    "## Part 5：ATR（平均真实波幅）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.1 ATR原理\n",
    "\n",
    "**ATR（Average True Range）** 由Welles Wilder发明，用于衡量价格波动的真实幅度，量化市场波动性。\n",
    "\n",
    "**真实波幅（TR）计算公式**：\n",
    "```\n",
    "TR = max(\n",
    "    最高价 - 最低价,\n",
    "    |最高价 - 昨收|,\n",
    "    |最低价 - 昨收|\n",
    ")\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**ATR计算公式**：\n",
    "```\n",
    "ATR = TR的N日指数移动平均\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**常用参数**：N = 14\n",
    "\n",
    "**应用场景**：\n",
    "- 衡量波动性：ATR越高，波动性越大\n",
    "- 设置止损位：常用ATR的倍数（如2倍ATR）\n",
    "- 仓位管理：根据ATR调整仓位大小"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 5.2 实现ATR计算函数 ==========\n",
    "def calculate_atr(df, n=14):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算ATR指标\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：\n",
    "    - df: DataFrame，包含'high', 'low', 'close'列\n",
    "    - n: ATR周期，默认14\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回：\n",
    "    - atr: Series，ATR值\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 计算真实波幅（TR）\n",
    "    high_low = df['high'] - df['low']\n",
    "    high_close = np.abs(df['high'] - df['close'].shift(1))\n",
    "    low_close = np.abs(df['low'] - df['close'].shift(1))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 取三者最大值\n",
    "    tr = pd.concat([high_low, high_close, low_close], axis=1).max(axis=1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算ATR（使用指数移动平均）\n",
    "    atr = tr.ewm(span=n, adjust=False).mean()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return atr\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ ATR计算函数已定义\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ========== 5.3 计算ATR并添加到数据框 ==========\n",
    "df['ATR_14'] = calculate_atr(df, n=14)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ ATR计算完成\")\n",
    "print(f\"   ATR范围：{df['ATR_14'].min():.2f} ~ {df['ATR_14'].max():.2f} 元\")\n",
    "print(f\"   最新ATR：{df['ATR_14'].iloc[-1]:.2f} 元\")\n",
    "print(f\"   最新收盘价：{df['close'].iloc[-1]:.2f} 元\")\n",
    "print(f\"   ATR/收盘价比：{(df['ATR_14'].iloc[-1]/df['close'].iloc[-1]*100):.2f}%\")\n",
    "df[['trade_date', 'close', 'high', 'low', 'ATR_14']].tail(10)"
   ]
